Write a java program using ArrayList to display the following output:

LinkedList: [Java, Python, JavaScript, Kotlin]
Removed Element: Python
New LinkedList: [Java, JavaScript, Kotlin]

//Code here
import java.util.*;//code here
public class collection
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        LinkedList<String> a=new LinkedList<String>();
        a.add("Java");
        a.add("Python");
        a.add("JavaScript");
        a.add("Kotlin");
        System.out.println("Linkedlist: "+a);
        System.out.println("Removed Element: "+a.get(1));
        a.remove(1);
        System.out.println("New LinkedList: "+a);
    }
}
